<head>
<title>Columnist Suzanne Fields</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Suzanne Fields</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-fields.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>

<!-- insert photo here-->
<UL>
<li>August 28, 1996 <a href="http://www.washtimes.com/opinion/fields.html">Fumbling The Ball At The White House</a>
<li>August 11, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/fields.8-11.html">The Flight We Almost Took</a>
<li>August 4, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/fields.8-4.html">Conservatism Can Close Dole's Gender Gap</a>
<li>July 22, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/fields.7-28.html">The Shattered Fairy Tale of Charles and Diana</a>
<li>July 8, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/fields.7-14.html">Does Character Still Matter?</a>
<li>July 1, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/fields.7-7.html">Don't Cry For Hillary</a>
