<html>
<head>
<title>Kathleen Howley</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">
<center><h2>Kathleen Howley</h2></center>
<p>
<hr>
<p>
<p>
Kathleen Howley, a real estate columnist and business reporter for the Boston Globe, writes a weekly opinion column that is syndicated in Catholic newspapers around the country. In addition, her work has appeared in the Boston Herald, the National Catholic Register, Catholic World Report, Latin Mass Magazine, and the Wanderer.
<p>
