</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT16-B15-41</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000252-B018-181</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html 204.71.237.86 19970108122034 text/html 6811
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
