<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Wesley Pruden</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Wesley Pruden</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-pruden.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>

<!-- insert photo here-->

<UL>

<li>August 28, 1996 <a href="http://www.washtimes.com/politics/pruden.html">Smoking Out a Truce In The War On Drugs</a>
<LI>August 11, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.8-11.html">The New Dole Gets Some Old Advice</a>
<li>July 22, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.7-28.html">Dreamy Dreams For An August Morning</a>
<li>July 8, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.7-14.html">Let's Blame the Dead For the Scary Stuff</a>
<li>July 1, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.7-7.html">It's 1996, And We're All From Arkansas</a>
<li>June 24, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.6-30.html">A Familiar Odor From The Summer of '73</a>
<li>June 17, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.6-23.html">Trying to Beat Nothing With Not Very Much</a>
<li>June 10, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.6-16.html">The Limited Hangout at the White House</a>
<li>May 27, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.6-2.html">Learning Lessons, All of them Wrong</a>
<li>May 20, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.5_26.html">No Cheap Sentiment for his generation</a>
<li>May 13, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.5_19.html">Somewhere There's A Hero From Kansas</a>
<li>April 29, 1996 <a href="/wash_times/pruden.5_5.html">The Stern Rebuke of a Sunday-School Boy</a>
</ul>
<p><br>








