<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000252-B021-185</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/columnists/aipe/beck121796.html 204.71.237.86 19970108123250 text/html 5284
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
