Education Matierals.&quot;  Press Release. Substance Abuse and
Mental Health Services Administration.  U.S. Department of Health
and Human Services. September 12, 1995. 
<P>
<li>&quot;Monitoring the Future Study: Trends in Prevalence of Various
Drugs for 8th Graders, 10th Graders, and High School Seniors.&quot;
NIDA Capsules, issued by the Press Office of the National Institute
on Drug Abuse. November 1994.
<P>
<li>&quot;National Drug Survey Results Released with New Youth Public
Education Materials.&quot; op. cit.
<P>
<li>Peggy Mann. &quot;Reasons to Oppose Legalizing Illegal Drugs.&quot;
Drug Awareness Information Newsletter. September 1988.
<P>
