<P>
18. Laurence Steingerg, Anne Fletcher and Nancy Darling. &quot;Parental
Monitoring and Peer Influences on Adolescent Substance Use.&quot;
<I>Pediatrics</I> Vol. 93, No. 6, June 1994: 1060-1064.
<P>
19. Bonnie Bonard. &quot;Fostering Resiliency in Kids: Protective
Factors in the Family, School, and Community.&quot;  Western Regional
Center Drug-Free Schools and Communities.  August 1991.
